# Folder Structure

This is a Next.js 16 + React 19 + Tailwind 4 + shadcn + Magic UI starter.

## Top-level

```text
app/                Next.js App Router pages
  demo/             Component showcase pages (do not delete)
components/
  ui/               shadcn primitives + ui/magic for Magic UI
  ui/magic/<group>/ Magic UI components, grouped by category (8 groups)
  demo/             Demo variants for every component
  demo/<...>/       mirrors components/ui/* (same folders, same filenames)
  showcase/         Internal showcase library (page, section, variant, tabs, code)
  providers.jsx     ThemeProvider + other client providers
docs/               Documentation (STRUCTURE, CONVENTIONS, ADDING-COMPONENTS, DEMO-SYSTEM, etc.)
docs/prompts/       Prompt templates for common AI tasks
hooks/              React hooks (kebab-case files)
lib/                Utilities (cn, etc.)
public/             Static assets
scripts/            Dev/scaffolding scripts (mjs)
```

## Module boundaries

- Pages in `app/demo/**` import demos from `@/components/demo` and the showcase
  library from `@/components/showcase`. Pages MUST NOT import directly from
  `@/components/ui`.
- Demo files in `components/demo/**` import the underlying component from
  `@/components/ui` (or `@/components/ui/magic`).
- Each leaf folder (`components/ui/magic/<group>`, `components/demo/<...>`) MUST
  have an `index.js` that re-exports each component file.

## Magic UI groups (mirrored across `ui/magic/*`, `demo/magic/*`, `app/demo/magic/*`)

`components`, `special-effects`, `animations`, `text`, `device`, `buttons`,
`backgrounds`, `community`. Use the same group name everywhere.

## When in doubt

- New shadcn primitive → `components/ui/<name>.jsx` + demo at
  `components/demo/components/<name>.jsx`.
- New Magic UI component → `components/ui/magic/<group>/<name>.jsx` + demo at
  `components/demo/magic/<group>/<name>.jsx`.
- New showcase helper → `components/showcase/<name>.jsx` + add to its `index.js`.
